706055f-a.title: Brooklyn: Newkirk Avenue - Nostrand Avenue
706055f-a.text:
Newkirk Ave., south side, west to Nostrand Ave. The trees mark the
southerly boundry of the Vanderveer Farm. The R.C. Church of St. Jerone
is seen in the background.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
